      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for that perfect, 'good-as-new' vibe without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
