    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This collector-grade example has undergone meticulous preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement with ARP bolts, and rear subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with a functioning variable M-differential for optimal torque distribution. Suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the telepathic steering response these chassis are renowned for. A truly turn-key, mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning purist.",
