      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its original purchase. The exterior boasts its original factory finish, free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, while the interior still carries that new-car aroma with leather surfaces that remain supple and uncreased. Every service milestone has been documented at the dealership, ensuring the mechanical components operate with the same precision as the day it rolled off the assembly line. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting its history as a fair-weather-only cruiser. From the crystal-clear headlight lenses to the untouched spare tire well, no detail has been overlooked. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it were brand new.",
